  <brief_title>Repeated Educational Intervention for the Prevention of Diabetic Foot Ulcers in High-risk Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Patient Education for the Prevention of Lower Limb Ulcers in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes: Validation of an Educational Intervention Repeated Every Three Months for 2 Years.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
