  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
    <is_fda_regulated_drug>No</is_fda_regulated_drug>
    <is_fda_regulated_device>No</is_fda_regulated_device>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Following a prior observation that a brief structured group educational intervention is
      effective for the prevention of diabetic foot ulcers in high-risk patients, but that the
      efficacy decreases over the time, this study is designed to verify the effect of a repetition
      of the educational intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
